v6D2LCbIpae0gM4Dq3ytUA">Lương Khải Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/M%C3%A3n-giang-h%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0u-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Chu-Th%E1%BB%8D-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-yXmi0TC5hbRA03_smomO1w">Mãn giang hồng - Lưu tặng Chu Thọ Xương - 滿江紅－留贈朱壽昌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Nguy%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-B%C4%83ng-H%E1%BB%93-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-c%C3%B4ng/poem-2dpOzokR-fjP60czehV8-Q">Nguyên nhật thướng Băng Hồ tướng công - 元日上冰壺相公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/Nh%E1%BA%ADm-Kh%C3%A2u-ng%E1%BB%99-V%C5%A9-t%C6%B0-t%C3%A2n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C6%A1-quy-t%E1%BB%B1-M%C3%A2n-Nam-d%C4%A9-m%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%AD-l%E1%BB%87-chi-ph%C3%A2n-h%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-YZ8n6uJCkCTgU3JQTZ7fFg">Nhậm Khâu ngộ Vũ tư tân Thượng Cơ quy tự Mân Nam dĩ mật tí lệ chi phân hướng - 任丘遇禹司賔尚基歸自閩南以蜜漬茘枝分餉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/author-9xzWBLqDsfopprRgu6Tsgg">Tra Thận Hành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/T%C3%A1n-%C6%AFng-Chu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C3%A0/poem-4paG9jIV1lW6aBM1oSPCvA">Tán Ưng Chuỷ trà - 讚鷹嘴茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/author-EjtGFCLaQR-cL2GZdcpbaQ">Lưu Vũ Tích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
